name: Bone
public_notice:
Bone has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. Visit this post for more information.
Old token page https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/bone-old.

description.en:
Leveraging the multimillion Dog Breeder and Pet Dog owner communities to improve Dog welfare, Dog Breeding and Dog knowledge. Using advanced technologies and a gamified reward system to make Dog care and welfare better.
Using immutable blockchain technology for Dog microchip identification and Dog life data, vaccination & immunization storage tracking
